<template>
</template>

<script>

	export default {
		name: 'echarts_test',
		data() {
	
			return {
			
			id:{
				type:String,
				default:'demo',
			}
				
	
			}
		},
		mounted() {
			this.drawLine();
		},
		methods: {
			drawLine(){
				let myChart = this.$echarts.init(document.getElementById(this.id))
				myChart.setOption({
					title:{text:"this is echarts00"},
					tooltip:{},
					xAxis:{data:["x1","x2","x3","x4"]},
					yAxis:{},
					series:[{
						name:'销量',
						type:'demo',
						data:[5,20,6,36,10,20]
					}]
				})
			},
		}
			
	
	}
</script>

<style>
</style>
